title: Dynamic Queue Survey

embed.description: Web survey powered by SurveyMonkey.com. Create your own online survey now with SurveyMonkey's expert certified FREE templates.

body:
Dynamic queue has been a long-standing feature-or at least enough for the community to have solid opinions on it.
Please fill out the survey if you have the time because I'm sure many people are curious to see how many people are actually satisfied by it?

[This is also for the people who may be afraid to speak out and say they like dynamic queue-the survey is anonymous]

replies.body:
